cff-version: 1.2.0
message: >-
  If you use this dataset in your research or work, please cite it using
  the metadata below.

title: AI TRiSM Market Index
abstract: >-
  A comprehensive, machine-readable open dataset covering the global market
  for AI Trust, Risk, and Security Management (AI TRiSM). The dataset indexes
  66+ vendors across 10 categories including AI governance platforms, runtime
  LLM security, explainability tools, red teaming, model monitoring, data
  privacy, content safety, and regulatory compliance. Includes market sizing
  data from 8 analyst firms, funding and M&A activity for 2022–2026, and
  a structured regulatory tracker for EU AI Act, NIST AI RMF, ISO 42001,
  GDPR, SR 11-7, and other global AI regulations. Updated automatically via
  GitHub Actions.

authors:
